{"tid":2168947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門通過法案　中國人與澳門人「平權」　中國人可做公務員捉澳人","createTime":"2020-08-22T06:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T14:26:35.000Z","uid":261647,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b49af375245d4a124eb94f85ed10a3dd925cb850","tid":2168947,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:22:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/macauconcealers/photos/a.158212900914486/3178157978919948/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmacauconcealers%2Fphotos%2Fa.158212900914486%2F3178157978919948%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThlBOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=59c58e64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/macauconcealers/photos/a.158212900914486/3178157978919948/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hT7Ndbg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhT7Ndbg.jpg&h=b73131c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【愛瞞報道】立會細則通過修改《司警局》法案 不排除非本地人擔任「秘密警察」<br />\n<br />\n立法會今（20日）細則性通過《修改司警局》法案，將於今年10月12日生效。法案新增的「秘密警察」條款最受爭議，特首日後有權按保安當局的需要豁免公開執行秘密職務的司警名單。<br />\n<br />\n．特首有權決定隱藏特定司警身分<br />\n<br />\n法案列明「基於人員安全的考量或執行特殊職務的需要，經適當說明理由」，行政長官可決定隱藏特定司警人員的身分。直選議員高天賜質疑，如「秘密警察」違規或濫用職權，市民如何舉報；而澳門只是彈丸之地，當局採取哪些措施隱藏有關人員身份。<br />\n<br />\n保安司司長黃少澤回應指，執法人員向市民執法前，必須先表明身份，否則市民可以反抗；至於當局如何隱藏人員身份，黃少澤沒有回應，以涉及技術層面為由不宜作討論，但聲稱當局已參考其他地區做法有充分的技術。<br />\n<br />\n．不排除非本地人成為「秘密警察」<br />\n<br />\n直選議員蘇嘉豪重申，公眾質疑當局可能濫用「秘密警察」條文，又認為條文中「執行特殊職務」的字眼空泛。黃少澤只重複如何執行豁免程序，沒有回應如何避免濫用「秘密警察」機制，只稱司法機關和市民都可以監督。<br />\n<br />\n蘇嘉豪又問到日後會否有非本地人依照政府個人勞動合同法律成為「秘密警察」，黃少澤承認有此法律規定，所有公務員包括「外僱公務員」享有權利一致，意味將來不排除會有非本地人成為「秘密警察」。他透露非本地人不會任職偵查員，但未有說明原因。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提，法案於立法會一般性表決時，直選議員吳國昌、區錦新、蘇嘉豪均投下反對票，而今日針對「秘密警察」條款作細則性表決時，只得蘇嘉豪和高天賜兩人投反對票，吳國昌和區錦新則改投贊成票。"},{"pid":"abdcdea37801caede16968f5110fedabec45abbb","tid":2168947,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"金融中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b20f7d764c2db8aa1a810689f2843adec6b079","tid":2168947,"uid":356218,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e11c7b5ba9e4e3107da4bc4824c5979bd1b17ea4","tid":2168947,"uid":254383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"出年香港都係咁"},{"pid":"bf2d049f0e48cf080d1964eb7268aaf6778d8142","tid":2168947,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4113c95909eb434d55fadf830c9f84ec09558c60","tid":2168947,"uid":34525,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"澳門人咁乖 點解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9784078d2b8dcb524eab03c608ae04b6b5d7fcf1","tid":2168947,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"澳門人會再乖d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc845f26ff57908d5091333479afb8f914e773e","tid":2168947,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"澳門人 明白什麼都總有限期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c371b57f514827089c19a6baa3c28132ea66bb6","tid":2168947,"uid":19527,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:32:25.000Z","msg":"唔搞事嘅澳門仲低賤過搞事嘅香港<br />\n點解嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f92099a853b7e3c6d0bdf170423b56d4b735486","tid":2168947,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:32:28.000Z","msg":"直選議員吳國昌、區錦新、蘇嘉豪均投下反對票，而今日針對「秘密警察」條款作細則性表決時，只得蘇嘉豪和高天賜兩人投反對票，<span class=\"red\">吳國昌和區錦新則改投贊成票。</span><br />\n<br />\n澳門版聞煮黨?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ea63d303a685d0c3e12e49ffd50127859788c6","tid":2168947,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67af29f9f1641827ae0fac68108b1ab9c78864f","tid":2168947,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9dc845f26ff57908d5091333479afb8f914e773e","tid":2168947,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"澳門人 明白什麼都總有限期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T14:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}